<li><strong>Access to Expertise</strong>: Collaborating with these bodies allows Ripple to tap into their extensive knowledge and expertise in regulatory matters. This helps Ripple stay updated with the latest regulatory developments and ensures that its remittance solutions are compliant with all applicable laws.</li>



